Summary: Biochemical reaction from quetiapine to quetiapine sulfoxide. This interaction is catalyzed by CYP3A4.
Biochemical reaction from quetiapine to 7-hydroxy quetiapine. This interaction is catalyzed by CYP2D6.
Biochemical reaction from norquetiapine to 7-hydroxy N-desalkylquetiapine. This interaction is catalyzed by CYP2D6.
Biochemical reaction from norquetiapine to N-desalkylquetiapine sulfoxide. This interaction is catalyzed by CYP3A4.
Biochemical reaction from quetiapine to norquetiapine. This interaction is catalyzed by CYP3A4.
